# USER STORIES:

## Authentications

1. As a **user** I can **create an account** so that I can **access all the site features**

2. As a **user** I can **login** so that I can **interact with the content available**

3. As a **user** I can **logout** so that I can **exit my account & prevent others from gaining access**

5. As an **admin** Ican **refresh access tokens** so that **users can remain logged in for 24h**

## Navigation	

6. As a **user** I can **view the navigation bar on every page** so that I can **easily navigate through the site**

7. As a **user** I can use **have infinite scroll** so that I can **continue to browse content without having to open a new page**

## Posts

8. As a **user** I can **create a new post**

9. As a **user** I can **view posts** so that I can **browse content**

10. As a **user** I can  **view post details** so that I can **obtain more information about a post**

11. As a **user** I can **like a post* so that i can instanly show my support on other content

12. As a **user** I can **view liked posts** so that I can ** see the posts I have previously liked and other's**

13. As a **user** I can **search posts** so that I can **find a post by user or title**
 
14. As a **user** I can **follow a users** so that I can **see the posts of the users I follow**

15. As a **user** I can **edit my post** so that I can **revise or change my content**

16. As a **user** I can **delete my post** so that I can **remove my content**

## Comments
17. As a **user** I can **create a comment**

19. As a **user** I can **view other comments**

20. As a **user** I can **edit my comment** so that I can **change or edit the information in the comment**

21. As a **user** I can **delete my comment** so that I can **remove it from the post**

##ofiles
22. As a **user** I would like to **view a profile page** so that I can **obtain more information about that user**
 - Story points: 1

23. As a **user** I would like to **see most popular profiles** so that I can **see who posts the most interesting content**
 - Story points: 2

24. As a **user** I would like to **see stats via a user profile** so that I can **see how many followers/following/comments they have**
 - Story points: 2

25. As a **user** I would like to **follow/unfollow a user** so that I can **keep tabs on users I like, or remove a user from my feed**
 - Story points: 1

26. As a **user** I would like to **view all posts by a user** so that I can **go through their previously published content**
 - Story points: 1

27. As a **user** I would like to **edit my profile** so that I can **update my personal details**
 - Story points: 2

28. As a **user** I would like to **update my username/password** so that I can **make alterations as needed**
 - Story points: 1

29. As a **user** I would like to **set my avatar** so that I can **assign a photo to my profile**
 - Story points: 3

30. As a **user** I would like to **view other users avatars** so that I can **quickly recognise another user**
 - Story points: 1

